---
title: Mushroom, Leek & Sliced Potato Filo Galette with Basil Pesto & Rocket Salad
description: When you put in the hard yards you want to be able to show off your creation and nothing looks as impressive as a
filo pastry galette. Everyone will ‘ooh’ and ‘ahh’ at the mushrooms and leek topped with fresh basil pesto. It’s a stellar
standout that will earn you admiration and praise!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
